Players & Progress

How to test
  1. Click a player card to focus them on the map.
  2. Copy a code from their card and paste it into Redeem Code below with their Player ID.
  3. Click a player dot on the map — the YSU penguin pops up with Name + ID + points and stays visible. Hover also previews it.
  4. Use more codes to move along the route. The LEADER is always shown at the top and haloed.
  5. Refresh the page — progress persists automatically.
